Instructions for gsutil:


gcloud init
gcloud auth configure-docker


Attach to node:

Step 1:
  Get container id
  
     docker ps -a

Step 2:
   Attach to container id. Here assume container id is b807c588c6f2
   
     docker exec -it b807c588c6f2 /bin/bash

